  "description": "Contamination detection and quantification at parts-per-trillion (ppt) levels: ICP-MS for metallic impurities (0.1-10 ppt detection), TOC analysis (<0.5 ppb), ion chromatography for anions/cations (<0.01 ppb), laser particle counting (0.05 μm), and dissolved oxygen monitoring (<0.1 ppb). Quality assurance framework with SEMI standard methods for electronic-grade chemical certification.",
